Photo by florence by mills on August 25, 2021. May be an image of bottle, cosmetics and text that says 'what is anti-blue light skin care? we made blue light protection skincare pretty simple with one ingredient: vegan plankton extract florence up in the clouds facial moisturizer zero chill makeup setting spray A florence episode 4: soak it in blue light protection toner filorence'.

Photo by florence by mills on August 25, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'what is anti-blue light skin care? natural planktonic material made of fresh-water algae species coming from the ancient lakes of the Auvergne volcanic region. over time the algae developed a protectivelaye of minerals and a source of silica found in acid lava coming from the core of the earth to help it reflect blue light. we specifically added plankton extract, a vegan algae, for its ability to help defend against the artificial blue light from your phone, TV, computer...'.
